abstract_str: the !!__stuhleners__!! were handed the wrong baby in a maternity ward mix-up . samantha __stuhlener__ had just given birth to baby levi at st vincent 's private hospital in melbourne . the wrong baby was brought to them from the settling room by a nurse . they spent 45 minutes with the couple 's baby before the nurse realised . the error comes despite both babies wearing the correct id wristbands . they are traumatised and claim to have had trouble bonding with levi . the hospital 's apology resulted in another embarrassing mix-up . the !!__stuhleners__!! received a letter which was addressed to the other couple involved - the parents of the other child .
